"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-celebrity-news-1933876-team-gb-athletes-children-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  The Paris Olympicshave welcomed thousands of athletes from across the world compete on the biggest stage, with many of their close family members supporting from the side lines.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992687663, \"rank\": 7.311021387368985e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A number of Team GB's athletes are proud parents, from the likes of diver Tom Daley and swimmer Adam Peaty, to silver medallist Amber Rutter and gymnast Max Whitlock.\", \"from\": 181, \"to\": 347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 193, \"end\": 200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.230848437398227e-17, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 255, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.375116181769495e-49, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 277, \"end\": 287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 334, \"end\": 346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Max Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One thing that has not gone unnoticed are their children who have made adorable appearances as their parents make sporting history - and let us be honest it's pretty adorable to watch.\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Adam Peaty  Olympic swimmer Adam is the father to his little boy, George, who he shares with ex-partner Eirianedd Munro.\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Munro\", \"score\": 0.9977356394113059, \"rank\": 0.002218740482037246, \"text\": \"Munro\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Munro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Munro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"George was born in 2020 and was seen cheering on his dad by the side of the pool.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Following his race where he won a silver medal, Adam said: \\\"When I hugged George, as soon as I saw his curly hair, I was gone, I was crying.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like I have been stung by a bee because I feel so swollen in my face from crying so much.\\\"\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 977, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Gabby Logan's preparations for Olympics revealed and one thing she 'never' does    Tom Daley  British diver Tom Daley shares two adorable children, Robbie and Phoenix, with his husband.\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 991, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabby_Logan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabby Logan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabby_Logan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabby_Logan\"}, {\"begin\": 1074, \"end\": 1083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/